snippet.title: SBK Generations - PC Gameplay 1080p
snippet.description:
SBK Generations - PC Gameplay 1080p

Subscribe here ►►► http://www.youtube.com/subscription_center?add_user=FirstPlaysHD
Also SHARE, COMMENT, LIKE ☺

Play through the last 4 seasons of the SBK world championships, including the new 2012 season to become world champion or test your skills in the new SBK Experience mode. With SBK Generations, Milestone has developed what they consider to be the definitive motorcycle game, filled with over 220+ riders, 60 bike models, 140+ teams, 17 circuits and up to 16 player online


░▒▓ PC Hardware ▓▒░

CPU: Intel Core i7 3770K @ 4.20 Ghz
RAM: 8 GB
GPU: ASUS GTX760-DC2OC-2GD5
OS:  Windows 7 64bit


░▒▓ Recording HW ▓▒░

Avermedia live Gamer HD
